cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is about person re-identification using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper proposes a novel deep self-paced learning algorithm, which involves updating sample weights based on both model age and sample loss. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves experiments on benchmark datasets, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
